==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Synchronal
<hw>Syn"chro*nal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Synchronous</er>.]</ety> <def>Happening at, or belonging to, the
same time; synchronous; simultaneous.</def> <rj><au>Dr. H.
More.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Synchronal</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Synchronal
<hw>Syn"chro*nal</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A synchronal thing or
event.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Synchronical</ent>⟦br⟧
